projectGridLines.title: Project 1 Title: Full Stack Developer
projectGridLines.description:
Project 1 Title: Full Stack Developer


Description: Responsible for development using mentioned technologies and

frameworks in diverse domains; Design competitive and performant application services

with a rich user experience.

Skill sets: Java Spring, NodeJS, Angular, HTML, CSS, SQL(postgres), NOSQL(Mongo)

and mobile frameworks, Understanding of application architecture, Sound knowledge of

full stack development and troubleshooting, understanding of complex system

architecture, components and requirements

Traits expectation: Highly innovative, systematic and capable of redefining solutions,

Self-driven, energetic, creative, with ability to work with teams
